 年以上有期徒\r\n刑；致重傷者，處 3 年以上 10 年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/CHDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c1179%2c20220712%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"CHDM,111,簡,1179,20220712,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"1179","JDATE":"20220712","JTITLE":"傷害"}